msgstr "ບໍລິສັດ."

#. module: spreadsheet_account
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet_account/static/src/accounting_functions.js:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The date range. Supported formats are \"21/12/2022\", \"Q1/2022\", "
"\"12/2022\", and \"2022\"."
msgstr ""
"ຊ່ວງວັນທີ. ຮູບແບບທີ່ຮອງຮັບແມ່ນ \"21/12/2022\", \"Q1/2022\", \"12/2022\", ແລະ "
"\"2022\"."

#. module: spreadsheet_account
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/spreadsheet_account/static/src/accounting_functions.js:0
#, python-format
